FEMALE (
allotype
): Total length 2.41. Book lung covers elliptical. Dorsal scutum anterior half without projecting denticles. Spine formula: tibia I v6-2-2, metatarsus I v3-2-1; tibia II v4-4-0, metatarsus II v3-2-0; tibia III p1-1-0, v0-1-0, metatarsus III p1-1-0, r0-1-0. Epigynal atrium narrow, with tubular median element (fig. 197).
